<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-2298] Wrong scaling of embedded type 1 font</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2298</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The file attached to &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-935&quot; title=&quot;Text not extracted with PDFBox 1.4&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-935&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-935&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; is rendered wrong. It seems that all embedded type1 fonts have the wrong scaling. All glyphs are to big and are overlapping.&lt;br/&gt;
It worked well before merging the no-awt branch into the trunk&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12738005">PDFBOX-2298</key>
            <summary>Wrong scaling of embedded type 1 font</summary>
